@Welcome to Gem Shooby
this is GEM SHOOBY 6000

$IMPORTANT NOTE
On some systems this is very unstable on
zzt 3.2 - use ClassicZoo instead.  You
can get the latest ClassicZoo here:
$https://zeta.asie.pl/wiki/

!y;I'm not on ClassicZoo.
:q
#endgame
#give health 2000
#clear db
#clear dc
#clear dd
#clear de
#clear df
#clear dg
#clear dh
#clear di
#clear dj
#clear dk
#clear dl
#clear dm
#clear dn
#clear do
#set da
:z
#end
:touch
Welcome to Gem Shooby
home of the gem shooby

!b;Instructions
#z
:b
Gem shooby how to play

Touch a shooby to get a gem.

Touch a shooby to turn the shooby into a
shooby for more gems.

Touch an ammo shooby for ammo.

Shoot a shooby with ammo for more ammo.

Buy a Shooby Shop to progress.

Buy Autoshooby for more shooby per shooby.

Buy Boost for more gems per shooby.

Buy Speed # for faster global cooldown.

Get the purple key.
!;Thank you I've seen enough bye
#end
:y
Would you like a failsafe set up in case
the object memory corrupts?

!x;Yes
!q;No need
#end
:x
$FAILSAFE ACTIVATED

If the board corrupts, just grab the key
and leave.  (And if you want to try it
later using ClassicZoo, that would be
awesome.)
!;k
#change purple door key
#q

    end
